{"tid":2512841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 蜜糖芥末炸雞定食","createTime":"2021-05-02T05:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T05:25:52.000Z","uid":33359,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f1b31f796025ee52bbf8b34e5b4c925864144e","tid":2512841,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJSh4p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJSh4p5.jpg&h=a0aa19df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pC4sHbO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpC4sHbO.jpg&h=c03cfd46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身想食另一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但竟然今日無開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩我係人稱 觀塘區最識兩手準備既男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即時去咗呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸雞是即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外層很香很脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉質嫩滑又多肉汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醬汁方面都加得岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飯是珍珠米<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個腳趾公好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一缺點係間鋪細咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b9110f4a9c855871aad25f2b65060fd8f90e8e","tid":2512841,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"遲食師"},{"pid":"b6c33973f39bb6e4c125c94a9abfa1f081068ed3","tid":2512841,"uid":321789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"C伏師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"